data.description: FANTASTIC LOCATION with this lovely estate on 10 lush and private acres! 2 ensuite primary BR's, 1 w/jetted tub and walk in shower and closet, the other w/full bath and private entrance to deck. Large kitchen is a chefs dream, real wood cabinets, granite countertops, SS appl; open concept combining the great room w/vaulted ceilings and a full length covered deck in back. Terrific for entertaining or just relax and enjoy the view of the pond and cedar trees. Formal dining w/a cozy breakfast nook complete the package. Oversized 2-car garage and 10x20 shed offers plenty of storage for equipment. Professionally landscaped, recently painted inside, newer exterior paint. 2022 furnace/heat pump, w/whole house filtration, 4 year old H2O tank.
